{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">More from 3block</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">New Age of Discovery</h2>Astro World is set in a future where humanity has begun colonizing new planets and is mining Astrium, a resource used as quantum fuel. You lead an expedition and must protect your colony by all means and get as many resources as possible.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979350/extras/Mine.gif?t=1736530073\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Defence</h2>Every night the colony is attacked by unknown creatures, so you have to build defenses and arm your colonists who will ensure the safety of your economic buildings.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979350/extras/Run.gif?t=1736530073\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Co-op for 1-4 players</h2>You're not going to another planet alone, are you?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Economy</h2>You must find a balance between defense and economy, by wisely spending the energy. Build various kinds of industrial buildings and upgrade them. Increase the number of colonists and supply them with the necessary equipment.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979350/extras/-1.gif?t=1736530073\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736530073","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979350/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736530073","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979350/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736530073","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979350/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736530073","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id